---
import '../styles/hero.css';
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero__grid">
    <div>
      <span class="hero__eyebrow">Go &middot; Apache-2.0 &middot; Redis Alternative &middot; In-Memory Database</span>
      <h1>Ultra-fast in-memory database alternative to Redis.</h1>
      <p class="hero__sub">
        Tellstone is a cloud-native in-memory database written in Go — a RESP2-compatible alternative to Redis with a zero-copy binary protocol and a shared-nothing architecture that eliminates scaling bottlenecks by utilizing every core on every machine. Currently supports <code>GET</code>/<code>SET</code>/<code>DEL</code>/<code>PING</code> over RESP2, with more commands on the roadmap. Best suited as an in-cluster cache or accelerator in front of a durable database.
      </p>

      <div class="hero__install">
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="tok-cmd">$</span>
        <code>git clone https://github.com/Saxy/Tellstone && task build</code>
        <button type="button" data-copy="git clone https://github.com/Saxy/Tellstone && task build" aria-label="Copy install command">
          copy
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/docs/getting-started/introduction/">Get Started</a>
        <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="https://github.com/Saxy/Tellstone">View on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero__illustration" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <filter id="coreGlow" x="-60%" y="-60%" width="220%" height="220%">
            <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="1.6" result="blur" />
            <feMerge>
              <feMergeNode in="blur" />
              <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic" />
            </feMerge>
          </filter>
        </defs>

        <!-- Outer facet + the six triangular facets, same mapping as the brand mark -->
        <path d="M 50 10 L 85 30 L 85 70 L 50 90 L 15 70 L 15 30 Z" fill="var(--slate-800)"/>
        <path d="M 50 50 L 15 30 L 50 10 Z" fill="var(--slate-600)" />
        <path d="M 50 50 L 50 10 L 85 30 Z" fill="var(--slate-700)" />
        <path d="M 50 50 L 85 30 L 85 70 Z" fill="var(--slate-800)" />
        <path d="M 50 50 L 85 70 L 50 90 Z" fill="var(--slate-900)" />
        <path d="M 50 50 L 50 90 L 15 70 Z" fill="var(--slate-800)" />
        <path d="M 50 50 L 15 70 L 15 30 Z" fill="var(--slate-700)" />

        <path d="M 50 20 L 75 35 L 75 65 L 50 80 L 25 65 L 25 35 Z" fill="none" stroke="var(--slate-600)" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.4"/>

        <g stroke="var(--cyan)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" filter="url(#coreGlow)">
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="22" />
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="78" />
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="22" y2="50" />
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="78" y2="50" />
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="30" y2="30" />
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="70" y2="30" />
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="70" y2="70" />
          <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="30" y2="70" />
          <line x1="50" y1="35" x2="65" y2="35" />
          <line x1="50" y1="65" x2="35" y2="65" />
          <line x1="35" y1="50" x2="35" y2="35" />
          <line x1="65" y1="50" x2="65" y2="65" />
        </g>

        <g fill="var(--cyan)">
          <circle class="node" style="animation-delay:0s" cx="50" cy="22" r="2" />
          <circle class="node" style="animation-delay:0.5s" cx="50" cy="78" r="2" />
          <circle class="node" style="animation-delay:1s" cx="30" cy="30" r="2" />
          <circle class="node" style="animation-delay:1.5s" cx="70" cy="30" r="2" />
          <circle class="node" style="animation-delay:2s" cx="70" cy="70" r="2" />
          <circle class="node" style="animation-delay:2.5s" cx="30" cy="70" r="2" />
          <circle cx="65" cy="35" r="1.5" />
          <circle cx="35" cy="65" r="1.5" />
        </g>

        <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="9" fill="var(--slate-900)" stroke="var(--cyan)" stroke-width="2.5" filter="url(#coreGlow)" />
        <circle class="core" cx="50" cy="50" r="4" fill="var(--cyan)" filter="url(#coreGlow)" />

        <style>
          .node, .core {
            animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
            transform-origin: center;
            transform-box: fill-box;
          }
          @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.55; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.3); }
          }
          @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
            .node, .core { animation: none; }
          }
        </style>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
  document.querySelectorAll('[data-copy]').forEach((btn) => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
      const text = btn.getAttribute('data-copy') ?? '';
      try {
        await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
        const original = btn.textContent;
        btn.textContent = 'copied';
        setTimeout(() => (btn.textContent = original), 1400);
      } catch {
        /* clipboard unavailable — no-op */
      }
    });
  });
</script>
